    "excerpt": "A mi sheberakh prayer by Rabbi Esteban Gottfried for the parents of students leaving school for their summer break. . . .",
    "content": "<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nמִי שֶׁבֵּרֵךְ אֲבוֹתֵינוּ אַבְרָהָם יִצְחָק וְיַעֲקֹב<br />\nוְאִמּוֹתֵינוּ שָׂרָה רִבְקָה רָחֵל וְלֵאָה,<br />\nהוּא יְבָרֵךְ אֶת כָּל יַלְדֵי יִשְׂרָאֵל הַיּוֹצְאִים לְחֻפְשָׁתָם הַשְּׁנָתִית,<br />\nוְאֶת כָּל הַמּוֹרִים וְהַהוֹרִים הַמְּסַיְּמִים יַחַד אִתַּם אֶת שְׁנַת הַלִּמּוּדִים.<br />\nיְהִי רָצוֹן מִלְּפָנֶיךָ שֶׁתּוֹלִיכֵם לְשָׁלוֹם וְתַצְעִידֵם לְשָׁלוֹם<br />\nוְתַגִיעַם לִשְׁנַת הַלִּמּוּדִים הַבָּאָה לְאַחַר מְנוּחָה וּבְכוֹחוֹת מְחֻדָּשִׁים.‏<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nMay he who blessed our forefathers Abraham, Isaac and Jacob<br />\nand our foremothers Sarah, Rivkah, Rachel and Leah<br />\nbless all of us, the students, as we go out to our yearly vacation,<br />\nand all of our parents and teachers who are finishing the school year with us.<br />\nWe hope that you will let us walk in peace and guide us in peace,<br />\nand bring us back to the next school year after rest and with renewed insight.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nמְקוֹר הַבְּרָכָה יַעֲנִיק לָהֶם בִּינָה וְדַעַת<br />\nלְהַמְשִׁיךְ לִצְמֹחַ,<br />\nלְהִסְתַּקְרֵן, לִלְמֹד וְלַחֲקֹר אֶת הָעוֹלָם<br />\nלְפִי קִצְבָּם,<br />\nוְיוֹסִיפוּ לְגַלּוֹת אֶת יְפִי הָעוֹלָם<br />\nדֶּרֶך עֵינַיִם מְלֵאוֹת פְּלִיאָה<br />\nוְלֵב מְלֵא חֶסֶד.‏<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nMay the source of blessing give us wisdom and knowledge<br />\nso we can continue to grow,<br />\ninvestigate, learn, and explore the world<br />\nat our pace,<br />\nand may we continue to discover the beauty of the world<br />\nthrough eyes full of wonder<br />\nand a heart full of loving-kindness.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nיְבָרֶכְךָ יְהוָֹה, וְיִשְׁמְרֶךָ<br />\nיָאֵר יְהוָֹה פָּנָיו אֵלֶיךָ, וִיחֻנֶּךָּ<br />\nיִשָּׂא יְהוָֹה פָּנָיו אֵלֶיךָ, וְיָשֵׂם לְךָ שָׁלוֹם.‏<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nMay YHVH bless you and guard you.<br />\nMay YHVH make their face shed light upon you and be gracious unto you.<br />\nMay YHVH lift up their face unto you and give you peace.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Numbers 6:23-27&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_conta